# Fukoku Life Insurance - Design System & Project Context

## Project Context

This project involves designing UI screens for **Fukoku Life Insurance (フコク生命)** using the Paper design tool via MCP.

- The app is an **agent-facing CRM tool** for insurance agents to manage prospects and existing customers
- "Hanako Fukoku (福国 花子)" is an example **prospect** (見込み客), not the app user
- The agent is the user -- they view customer profiles, track info-gathering progress, assess risks, and create proposals

## Brand Colors (from Fukoku Life corporate identity)

- **Fukoku Purple** (logo ribbon): `#9B8AAE` / lighter `#B5AAC8` / bg `#F0E8F5`
- **Corporate Red**: `#C41E2E` / `#9E1824` (dark)

